gw.plugin.util

Class SequenceUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.plugin.util.SequenceUtil

  • public abstract class SequenceUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility for generating unique values from a sequence. The values are unique within your application, e.g. unique across all nodes in your cluster.
